🗝️ 📚
🧩 derivative(xs) 👉
   長さ ⬅️ 📐 xs
   結果 ⬅️ []
   i ⬅️ 1
   上限 ⬅️ 差(長さ, 1)
   🌀 上限 👉
      値 ⬅️ xs[i]
      微分値 ⬅️ 積(i, 値)
      結果 🧲 微分値
      i ⬆️
   🔚
   ✅ 結果
🔚
>>> derivative([3, 1, 2, 4, 5]) 
[1, 4, 12, 20]
>>> derivative([1, 2, 3]) 
[2, 6]
>>> derivative([3, 1, 2, 4, 5]) 
[1, 4, 12, 20]
>>> derivative([1, 2, 3]) 
[2, 6]
>>> derivative([3, 2, 1]) 
[2, 2]
>>> derivative([3, 2, 1, 0, 4]) 
[2, 2, 0, 16]
>>> derivative([1]) 
[]